---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About Us" description="Learn about AI Tools Hub - your trusted source for AI tool reviews and guides.">
  <section class="py-12">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">About AI Tools Hub</h1>

      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">
          AI Tools Hub is your trusted source for honest, in-depth reviews of AI tools. We help creators, developers, and businesses find the right AI solutions for their needs.
        </p>

        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
        <p>
          With hundreds of AI tools launching every month, it's harder than ever to find the right one. We test, compare, and review AI tools so you don't have to waste time and money on tools that don't deliver.
        </p>

        <h2>How We Review</h2>
        <p>
          Every tool on our site goes through a thorough evaluation process:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Hands-on Testing:</strong> We actually use each tool for real projects</li>
          <li><strong>Feature Analysis:</strong> We evaluate all key features and capabilities</li>
          <li><strong>Pricing Review:</strong> We assess value for money</li>
          <li><strong>Support Testing:</strong> We test customer support responsiveness</li>
          <li><strong>Output Quality:</strong> We evaluate the quality of AI-generated content</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Affiliate Disclosure</h2>
        <p>
          We use affiliate links on this site. When you click a link and make a purchase, we may earn a commission at no extra cost to you. This helps support our work and allows us to continue providing free, honest reviews.
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>Our commitment:</strong> Affiliate relationships never influence our reviews or ratings. We only recommend tools we genuinely believe in.
        </p>

        <h2>Our Team</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 not-prose">
          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-6">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <span class="text-2xl">👨‍💻</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-lg">Alex Chen</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Founder & Lead Reviewer</p>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mt-2 text-sm">5+ years in AI/ML, former product manager at a Fortune 500 company.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-6">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <span class="text-2xl">👩‍💼</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-lg">Sarah Johnson</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Content Director</p>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mt-2 text-sm">Content marketing specialist with a focus on AI-powered workflows.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2>Contact Us</h2>
        <p>
          Have questions or suggestions? We'd love to hear from you.
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>📧 Email: hello@aitoolshub.com</li>
          <li>🐦 Twitter: @aitoolshub</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
